# This folder will contain the following artifacts after training:
#
#   diffusion_photo_restorer_epoch_1.pth
#   diffusion_photo_restorer_epoch_2.pth
#   ...                                      ← UNet2D state dicts, one per epoch
#   diffusion_photo_restorer_epoch_10.pth
#
#   diffusion_photo_restorer/
#   └── logs/                               ← TensorBoard training logs
#
#   restored_output.jpg                     ← Output from inference.py
#
# Run:  python "src/Diffusion model/train.py"     to generate weights
#       python "src/Diffusion model/inference.py"  to generate restored_output.jpg
